      <title>[부음] 이우재 전 체신부장관 별세 외</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2024/07/13/TJLFQF6K4FDZHAT5UI5PC4QHEI/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2024/07/13/TJLFQF6K4FDZHAT5UI5PC4QHEI/</guid>
